import React from "react";
import { StatusBar } from "expo-status-bar";
import { StyleSheet, TouchableOpacity, Text, View } from "react-native";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
      <StatusBar style="auto" />
      <View style="styles.container_keys">
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>1</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>2</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>3</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>4</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>5</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>6</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>7</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>8</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>9</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>10</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>5</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text style={styles.keys}>5</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    backgroundColor: "#aaa",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
  },
  keys: {
    display: "flex",
    backgroundColor: "#f00",
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center",
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderColor: "#aaa",
    fontSize: 30,
    color: "#fff",
    width: 100,
    height: 100,
  },
  container_keys : {
    display: 'flex',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    flexDirection: 'row',

  }
});
